  "detailed_description": "Hexxon is a logic puzzle game about connecting hexagons using primary and secondary colors.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 70 brain-teasing puzzles<br></li><li> Progress on a level is saved, so you can come back to it later<br></li><li> Relaxing, atmospheric soundtrack<br></li><li> 3 hints allotted per level in case you get stumped<br></li><li> Built-in level editor -- make and share your own levels!</li></ul>",
